At least 21 people, including 19 students, were killed in the mass shooting at an elementary school in Texas on May 24. As tragic mass shootings are becoming more common, U.S. President Joe Biden is calling for an immediate control on guns. But what a never-ending wrangling behind the scenes! Editor: Yuan Xin Chief editor: Ge Jing Managing director: Mei Yan (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)